location.fullValue: Thrive Monterrey Plan, Hidden Lake East

data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the hidden lake subdivision! This stunning low maintenance home was built in 2020 and offers everything you need for comfortable and modern living. Featuring 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This home is perfect for families looking for a home close to all the amenities. This home sits within a few miles of SEH. Once you step into the home you'll fall in love with the beautiful open concept design.  The kitchen is perfect for someone who loves to entertain, complete with stainless steel appliances, large kitchen island and granite countertops. Schedule your appointment to view this stunning home today!
